This house has been updated with newer windows 97, gutters 15, Steel siding (with transferable lifetime warranty against hail) new furnace 17, new A/C 17. A huge bedroom in the lower level and an unfinished bathroom ready to add your style and equity, possible to make a master walk through bathroom. Nice backyard that backs up to the city park. Home is ready for your outdoor lifestyle. Garden shed built to last.

For sale: $274,900. This house boasts 9' ceilings, original breathtaking ornate woodwork, along with hardwood floors, a built-in china hutch and bookcases with leaded glass doors. There are large three season porches on the front and back of the home, including a sun porch on the 2nd level. All appliances are in great working condition, and most are less than 5 years old. There are many extras, too numerous to mention! This home is a must see, with its unique windows and architectural design from days gone by. It offers character not seen in homes of today. You won't be disappointed!
Zestimate® Home Value: $200,527.

For sale: $332,900. Under construction four level conveniently located close to shopping, schools, parks and freeway access. Spacious open main level living spaces with vaulted ceilings and a ceiling fan. Enjoy upgraded rustic maple kitchen cabinetry, knock down ceilings, white trim and 3 panel doors. Additional staircase leads from the back of the garage to the third level laundry area. This creates a nice mud room to help keep messes out of your living spaces. The master suite features a spacious walk-in closet and private master bathroom with a linen closet. Second bedroom boasts a walk-in closet as well. Landscape allowance is included in the price.

For sale: $289,900. Highly sought after, move-in ready walkout rambler on the Monticello Golf Course! Lower level has 2 bedrooms, 3/4 bath and family room with wet bar for entertaining. Large storage/utility room. Roof, garage floor, siding on front of house and retaining wall in back were all replaced in 11/2011. New A/C in 2019. One year home warranty included.

Welcome to your new ?stay-cation? golf villa! Located on the Riverwood National 18 Hole Golf Course, is where you?ll find this stunning nearly new 2017 built detached townhome golf villa with all the upgrades!  It is fully finished with 2,438 square feet , a walkout rambler style townhome with main level living (plus finished lower level) and situated on one of the larger lots in this neighborhood, on a culdesac with direct access and back views of Hole 9 and front views of Hole 1! The property is within close proximity to the clubhouse, parks, the Mississippi River, the Albertville Outlet Mall, dining options, conveniences and Hwy 101 and I-94!  Call it home today!!

This home was built in 2017 by local builder Crestwood Homes and includes a covered front entry, beautiful landscaping, irrigated yard and an insulated, heated & epoxied floor 2 car main level garage, plus a convenient tuckunder 3rd stall golf cart garage off the back lower level.  There is also a partially covered main level deck and lower level paver patio, both with golf course views. Home includes gutters, concrete driveway & fully landscaped. 

Walk in from the covered front entry to the welcoming spacious foyer with direct access to the front bedroom/office and main level guest full bathroom.  The main level features an open floor plan with wood floors throughout foyer, kitchen, dining and living room. The kitchen features medium stained cabinetry accented with glass tile backsplash, granite counters, oil rubbed bronze hardware, center angled island, pendant, recessed & under-cabinet lighting, stainless steel appliances including a gas range and a walk-in pantry. Informal dining has sliding glass doors with which leads to the covered deck.  The living room features corner gas fireplace with floor to ceiling stone surround and breath-taking golf course views. The master bedroom has a ceiling fan, neutral carpet, trayed ceiling and a private master bathroom with walk-in tiled shower, tiled floors, double custom vanity with granite tops, natural light window in bath and walk-in closet and separate water closet with pocket door.  The main level living also includes a separate laundry room with front load washer and dryer and built in cabinetry, plus a mudroom off the garage with custom bench seating and coat closet.  All 2 paneled stained doors and white trim throughout. 

The walkout lower level is fully finished with huge family room with 2nd gas fireplace with stone surround, separate dedicated home gym area with French doors, a 3rd bedroom, a full bathroom, a very spacious mechanical room with loads of storage area and an awesome golf cart garage (or storage area or workshop area?you choose!)

description:
Recently sold: $262,000. Imagine the entertaining possibilities in this 4-level home with a large 2-level deck! The deck overlooks the private yard surrounded by pine trees. This house is in a great location with Pioneer park just around the corner and the high school only 1/2 mile away. Pioneer park has a large play area, volleyball court, pavilion, and nature trails. 

This 4-level home has 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, a 3 car garage, and a large 2-level deck. The kitchen, living room, and dining room have vaulted ceilings and the appliances are stainless steel. The upper level has 3 bedrooms and the master bedroom features a walk-in closet. The main level family room has a gas fireplace and access to the deck. The lower-level has a large bedroom and a 3/4 bath.

This house is being sold as a rent-to-own.

description:
Recently sold: $445,000. *Executive rambler overlooking the gorgeous Riverwood National Golf Course! From your backyard you can walk out to the 2nd hole tee box and enjoy a day of golf! Home is also just minutes from Vintage Golf Course and close to the Mississippi River where you can enjoy fishing, boating, swimming and canoeing along with many parks trail ways including Mississippi River Trail and Otsego County Park for miles of hiking, biking and walking trails along with picnic and play areas.

*The home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and 3,794 FSF and includes upgraded amenities like vaulted and knock down ceilings, hardwood and tile flooring, 6 panel doors, decorative ledges, arches, niches and pillars, raised panel cabinetry, wall and ceiling speakers throughout, security system and much more!

*Enjoy your morning coffee on the covered front porch. From the welcoming foyer glass French doors welcome you into a convenient home office. The large bright and sunny great room features a built-in entertainment center, cozy gas fireplace with tile and wood surround and decorative niche and a patio door that leads to the outdoor deck for those family barbecues or for enjoying golf course views. Prepare family dinners in the beautiful gourmet kitchen which features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry, raised panel cabinetry, center island, high top breakfast bar and an additional breakfast bar that faces the adjoining dining room.

*The 2 main level bedrooms both overlook the golf course and the master suite features a box vaulted ceiling with cove molding, his and hers closets and a private master bathroom with double bowl vanity, separate toilet room and corner tile shower with custom glass door, step up whirlpool tub with tile surround and decorative pillars, linen closet, towel warming drawer and tile flooring. There is also a main level laundry/mud room and another full bathroom.

*The spacious lower level family room with room for a billiard table is perfect for entertaining and also features a beautiful wet bar area with hardwood flooring and granite countertops. There are 2 additional bedrooms, both with walk-in closets, and an office/game room, and a ¾ bathroom with tile shower with glass door, granite top with glass tile backsplash, vessel sink, and tile flooring.

*The home is situated on a beautifully maintained walk-out lot with concrete patio, many rock and plant gardens, in-ground sprinkler system and a 3 car attached garage with opener. Great location close to schools, parks, restaurants, and shopping and just minutes from Albertville Outlet Mall and Highways 94, 10 and 101 for a quick commute!
